{"type": "article", "id": 23108, "title": "巧克力店Journey Club的平面设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-02T07:30:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153725OdxK7nRU4sqGu86F.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">The Cacao Journey Club 是中美洲厄瓜多尔的巧克力店和供应商，他们和当地设计师 Santiago Landaburü 都认为，巧克力是上天给当地的礼物，在设计 logo 时就用了可可豆的元素，是一个大的被剥开的可可豆。一种形式是在白底上描黑线，另一种在黑底上用金色的图案填充，可以见到清晰纹路和立体质感，很有辨识度。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061537230mfjx9kvP3ZrKHh5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.60096931\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153723P4jqSTHLm0utJiXQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153723ly5gVGOCHDNbPoxp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153724kx6Zth1r0XdqRTfK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153724S6T0hKR9X2luVqHW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}